CORBIN v. WARDEN OF MARYLAND PENITENTIARY [App. No. 31,

September Term, 1960.]

Decided November 15, 1960.

*680Before Bruñe, C. J., and Henderson, Hammond, Prescott and Horney, JJ.

Per Curiam.

For the reasons stated by Judge Harlan for denying relief in his opinion filed in the Criminal Court of Baltimore, application for leave to appeal is denied.

Application denied.
